## Base URL
BASE_URL_DEMO_APP

## Request 1 - GET Daftar Data
GET/http:127.0.0:8088/api/users

Penjelasan:
- Method: GET
- Tujuan: Mengambil daftar data user
- Expected status code: 200 OK

## Request 2 - GET Detail Data
GET/http:127.0.0:8088/api/users/2

Penjelasan:
- Method: GET
- Tujuan: Mengambil detail data user berdasarkan ID
- Expected status code: 200 OK

## Request 3 - POST Tambah Data
POST/http:127.0.0:8088/api/users
{"username": "data.student", "email": "data.student@example.edu", "role": "student", "status": "active", "department": "Sains Data"}

Penjelasan:
- Method: POST
- Tujuan: Menambahkan data user baru
- Header penting: Content-Type: application/json
- Expected status code: 201 Created atau 200 OK

## Request 4 - Patch Update Data
PATCH/http:127.0.0:8088/api/users/1
{"status": "inactive"}

Penjelasan:
- Method: POST
- Tujuan: Mengirim perubahan data produk
- Header penting: Content-Type: application/json
- Expected status code: 200 OK
